title: Duzzit Cool Linen Bathroom Cleaning Mousse
features: FAST CLEANING FOR BATHROOM SURFACES: Duzzit Bathroom Cleaning Mousse, easily removes soap scum, bathroom dirt, grime and toothpaste marks, leaving the bathroom surfaces sparkling clean
SHOWERS & MORE!: Duzzit Bathroom Cleaning Mousse, cleans, showers, bathtubs, sinks and tiles. Easy cleaning, minimum effort, with a fresh Cool Linen scent
QUICK & EASY TO USE: Duzzit Bathroom Cleaning Mousse, powerful formula, quickly and easily spray small or larger areas of the bathroom, wipes and rise, leaving a sparkling finish and fresh scent

POWER CLEANING: Duzzit Bathroom Cleaning Mousse, used daily helps prevent limescale build up. Shake can well before use. Hold the can upside down. Spray the mousse onto the surface at a distance of 15-25cm. Leave for 5-10 minutes to allow the cleaning action to work. Wipe with a clean cloth and rinse well with water
